      <title>为什么巧克力世界陷入危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/why-there-is-chocolate-crisis-and-what-s-happening-to-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巧克力世界正面临如此严重的可可短缺，以至于疯狂的交易吸引了一个不太可能的参与者：皮埃尔·安杜兰德（Pierre Andurand），一位以押注石油而闻名的对冲基金经理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/why-there-is-chocolate-crisis-and-what-s-happening-to-prices</guid>
